@startuml
title TPM virtual smartcard deployment

start
:Install / configure a Certificate Authority (CA);
:Create a certificate template for smartcard logon;
:Publish (allow) the template on the CA;
:Create the TPM virtual smartcard on the device\n(tpmvscmgr create);
:Enroll the logon certificate onto the\nTPM virtual smartcard;
if (TPM present and provisioned?) then (yes)
  :Key pair generated and sealed in the TPM;
  :User logs on with PIN against the\n"always-inserted" virtual card;
  stop
else (no)
  :Deployment fails\n(no hardware-backed key store);
  stop
endif
@enduml
